的大逃杀中，参与者必须在一个封闭的孤立岛屿上生存几天。随着空间逐渐变小，发生了一系列动荡的事态发展，包括参与者走出区域并在爆炸中丧生，以及他们所组成的团队内部发生背叛。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="#Vtuber 大逃杀" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mb8Voo597zI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="#Vtuber 大逃杀 2" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aRKqrORmEU0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="#Vtuber Battle Royale 3 Nijisanji Special" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0cVCnGsbmrE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了在第1集到第3集中崭露头角的成员之外，这次的参与者还包括<a href="https://twitter.com/itolife" target="_blank" rel="noopener">伊藤生活</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/Haneru_Inaba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">稻叶羽流</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/meikahaotoko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">歌名花</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/Sara_Hoshikawa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星川沙罗</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/yukokuroberu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">罗贝尔佑五郎</a>。参与成员名单如下。</p><blockquote><p>・<a href="https://twitter.com/itolife" target="_blank" rel="noopener">伊藤生活</a><br />・<a href="https://twitter.com/Haneru_Inaba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">稻叶羽流</a><br />・<a href="https://twitter.com/meikahaotoko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">歌衣制造商</a><br />・<a href="https://twitter.com/debidebiru_sama" target="_blank" rel="noopener">德比德比・德比鲁</a><br />・<a href="https://twitter.com/siroyoutuber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网络少女白</a><br />・<a href="https://twitter.com/tomari_mari" target="_blank" rel="noopener">马里·乌萨马里</a><br />・<a 